metadata.name: Juicebox Studios #1
metadata.description:
Juicebox Studios is a stake-able token that grants you access to one of the very first web2.5 brands.
With 1,111 Juicebox Studios in our collection, there’s plenty to go around.
Place your Juicebox Studios in the ‘fridge’ to earn SIP daily and claim rewards from the Juicebox Studios storefront.

Grab a Juicebox and start sippin’.
